overview.en: The ALCT team has more than 5 blockchain industry experts who come to Uber, Google, KAYAK, LinkedIn and Deloitte and other world top universities or internationally well-known companies, including some of them have received international honor members, and ALCT has established offices in Beijing, San Francisco, New York and Singapore.
overview.zh: ALCT 是基于区块链的去中心化，它的技术架构跟传统通讯网络不同，传统的通讯网络都是基于中心服务器建立，进行数据交换，并建立实现数据流连接。而ALCT完全是基于分布式的通讯网络，完全切除中心服务器，以实现对传统通讯方式的全面革新。
